1. s-bsdipa example
-------------------

  $ file .1 .2
  .1: troff or preprocessor input, ASCII text
  .2: troff or preprocessor input, ASCII text

The manuals of S-nail, v14.9.25 vs v14.10.0-alpha.

  $ ll .1 .2
  -rw-r----- 1 steffen steffen 428420 Apr 24 19:36 .1
  -rw-r----- 1 steffen steffen 390770 Apr 24 19:36 .2

  $ for c in -J -j -Z -z; do
      for b in 32 64; do
        echo $b/$c
        ./s-bsdipa$b $c -9 diff .2 .1 .P$b$c
        ./s-bsdipa$b $c -f diff .2 .1 .P$b$c
        ./s-bsdipa$b $c -f7 diff .2 .1 .P$b$c
        ./s-bsdipa$b patch .1 .P$b$c .R$b$c
      done
    done

